                <h1>Customize Dual Monitor Backgrounds Easily</h1>
                <p>To have two distinct backgrounds on dual monitors, start by right-clicking your desktop and selecting 'Display Settings'. Ensure both monitors are detected. Choose one monitor and click 'Background'. Set your preferred image or color. Repeat for the other monitor. Now, enjoy a personalized dual display experience!</p>
